WEBVTT

00:00:54.320 --> 00:00:55.119
What a witch.

00:00:55.479 --> 00:00:56.560
You just know how to steal men.

00:00:56.719 --> 00:00:58.479
You knew Harun was my boyfriend, yet you tried to steal him.

00:01:00.320 --> 00:01:00.840
Let go.

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:15.519
Teacher.

00:01:16.799 --> 00:01:17.920
What is going on here?

00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:20.760
It's just like I told you on the phone.

00:01:21.239 --> 00:01:22.760
Your daughter and her,

00:01:23.680 --> 00:01:24.760
the two of them together,

00:01:24.920 --> 00:01:26.239
pushed their classmate Zhao Li

00:01:26.439 --> 00:01:28.280
down the stairs.

00:01:29.079 --> 00:01:30.200
I didn't.

00:01:30.519 --> 00:01:32.359
She fell down by accident herself.

00:01:32.959 --> 00:01:33.519
You shut up.

00:01:33.519 --> 00:01:35.480
Zhao Li has already been sent to the hospital.

00:01:35.760 --> 00:01:36.840
Her parents have rushed over there too.

00:01:37.439 --> 00:01:38.120
I advise you

00:01:38.439 --> 00:01:39.920
to hurry to the hospital and visit her.

00:01:40.200 --> 00:01:41.760
Apologize to them properly.

00:01:42.239 --> 00:01:43.319
And pay whatever compensation is needed.

00:01:43.519 --> 00:01:44.319
As for your daughter,

00:01:45.040 --> 00:01:46.959
take her home first and discipline her properly.

00:01:47.519 --> 00:01:49.359
Regarding the punishment, the School Committee and I

00:01:49.400 --> 00:01:51.560
will notify you after we reach a decision.

00:01:52.599 --> 00:01:53.079
Teacher.

00:01:54.959 --> 00:01:56.640
Hurry up and apologize to the teacher, admit your mistake.

00:01:56.879 --> 00:01:57.560
Hurry up.

00:01:57.760 --> 00:01:58.840
It really wasn't me.

00:01:58.840 --> 00:02:00.319
She was the one bullying people first.

00:02:00.599 --> 00:02:02.120
Why do I have to apologize?

00:02:02.480 --> 00:02:03.000
Teacher.

00:02:03.560 --> 00:02:05.359
Look, my daughter says she didn't push her.

00:02:05.680 --> 00:02:07.680
Is there some misunderstanding here?

00:02:07.959 --> 00:02:10.800
Many students saw it with their own eyes and can testify.

00:02:11.199 --> 00:02:12.120
You can't deny it.

00:02:12.520 --> 00:02:13.919
Are you still trying to make excuses?

00:02:14.439 --> 00:02:15.560
Teacher, we admit our mistake.

00:02:17.360 --> 00:02:18.599
We sincerely apologize, Teacher.

00:02:19.960 --> 00:02:20.520
I'm sorry.

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:28.479
Teacher

00:02:31.479 --> 00:02:32.039
Nana

00:02:32.599 --> 00:02:33.240
Nana

00:02:35.719 --> 00:02:36.360
Nana

00:02:36.960 --> 00:02:37.719
Auntie

00:02:39.400 --> 00:02:40.039
Li Ren

00:02:44.159 --> 00:02:44.800
Auntie

00:02:46.080 --> 00:02:47.360
I can take all the responsibility.

00:02:47.360 --> 00:02:49.080
Tell them I was the one who pushed her.

00:02:49.520 --> 00:02:51.000
Our Nana is very well-behaved.

00:02:51.080 --> 00:02:52.199
She wouldn't do such a thing.

00:02:52.199 --> 00:02:53.120
As long as you are willing to cover

00:02:53.120 --> 00:02:54.319
all of Zhao Li's medical expenses,

00:02:54.319 --> 00:02:55.719
I can take the blame.

00:02:56.319 --> 00:02:57.199
I have no parents,

00:02:57.960 --> 00:02:58.800
and no money for compensation.

00:03:00.479 --> 00:03:02.159
I can accept all the punishment.

00:03:03.560 --> 00:03:05.080
Our Nana didn't push anyone.

00:03:05.080 --> 00:03:06.280
I pushed her all by myself.

00:03:06.680 --> 00:03:07.919
It has nothing to do with Nana.

00:03:08.439 --> 00:03:09.000
Okay.

00:03:09.560 --> 00:03:10.159
Nana...

00:03:11.159 --> 00:03:12.560
At that time, I was selfish.

00:03:13.439 --> 00:03:14.479
I didn't want my daughter

00:03:14.800 --> 00:03:16.319
to be disciplined and expelled.

00:03:17.039 --> 00:03:17.800
Afterwards,

00:03:18.240 --> 00:03:19.919
Li Ren was expelled from school

00:03:20.639 --> 00:03:21.879
and disappeared.

00:03:23.120 --> 00:03:25.919
Because Nana lost her good friend,

00:03:26.120 --> 00:03:27.479
she had no heart to study.

00:03:27.919 --> 00:03:29.120
Left with no choice,

00:03:29.599 --> 00:03:32.199
I had to transfer her to Tai Cheng.

00:03:33.879 --> 00:03:34.840
Unexpectedly,

00:03:35.240 --> 00:03:36.319
many years later,

00:03:37.560 --> 00:03:38.639
we met again.

00:03:38.960 --> 00:03:40.919
Auntie, long time no see.

00:03:41.319 --> 00:03:42.479
Li Ren.

00:03:43.639 --> 00:03:45.360
It's really been so many years.

00:03:45.479 --> 00:03:46.120
Yes.

00:03:46.879 --> 00:03:48.639
You've become more and more beautiful.

00:03:48.639 --> 00:03:49.520
Thank you, Auntie.

00:03:50.599 --> 00:03:51.280
Come, come, come.

00:03:51.280 --> 00:03:51.919
Just in time for dinner.

00:03:51.919 --> 00:03:52.400
Okay.

00:03:52.400 --> 00:03:52.919
Come, come.

00:03:52.919 --> 00:03:53.240
Sit down.

00:03:53.439 --> 00:03:54.080
Sit.

00:03:55.960 --> 00:03:57.280
So much good food.

00:03:58.840 --> 00:03:59.520
You...

00:03:59.599 --> 00:04:01.360
just in time to taste Auntie's cooking.

00:04:02.039 --> 00:04:02.599
Thank you.

00:04:03.360 --> 00:04:04.960
About that incident at school back then,

00:04:05.319 --> 00:04:07.520
Li Ren took all the blame alone.

00:04:08.280 --> 00:04:09.439
Actually, I felt very guilty inside.

00:04:09.439 --> 00:04:10.719
Come, have a chicken leg.

00:04:11.120 --> 00:04:12.080
Meeting again,

00:04:12.800 --> 00:04:13.680
I really wanted to make it up to her.

00:04:13.680 --> 00:04:14.439
Auntie,

00:04:14.840 --> 00:04:15.719
thank you.

00:04:16.519 --> 00:04:18.959
Actually, if you hadn't paid the compensation back then,

00:04:19.680 --> 00:04:21.399
I might have gone to prison.

00:04:22.120 --> 00:04:23.480
It's all in the past, let's not mention it.

00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:25.560
Come, eat more.

00:04:25.920 --> 00:04:27.680
Yes, it's all in the past.

00:04:27.680 --> 00:04:28.399
Let's not talk about it.

00:04:29.519 --> 00:04:30.160
Thank you, Auntie.

00:04:30.160 --> 00:04:30.879
That's too much, thanks.

00:04:30.879 --> 00:04:31.360
Mom.

00:04:31.680 --> 00:04:32.399
You know, now...

00:04:32.399 --> 00:04:33.920
you can't call her Li Ren anymore.

00:04:34.279 --> 00:04:36.079
She's a big internet celebrity now.

00:04:36.319 --> 00:04:37.199
Call her Di Fu.

00:04:37.560 --> 00:04:38.480
Di Fu.

00:04:39.360 --> 00:04:40.319
Sounds nice, sounds nice.

00:04:42.480 --> 00:04:44.600
Look, Di Fu hasn't been here for so many years.

00:04:44.879 --> 00:04:45.759
Go buy some wine quickly.

00:04:45.759 --> 00:04:46.720
Let's celebrate.

00:04:47.600 --> 00:04:48.000
Okay.

00:04:48.199 --> 00:04:48.879
We're having wine, Auntie?

00:04:48.879 --> 00:04:49.360
Just a moment.

00:04:49.800 --> 00:04:50.600
Have some wine.

00:04:51.360 --> 00:04:52.160
Okay.

00:04:55.800 --> 00:04:56.399
Di Fu.

00:04:57.279 --> 00:04:58.839
You and Nana are so close.

00:04:59.519 --> 00:05:01.319
She tells you everything, right?

00:05:03.000 --> 00:05:03.879
What's wrong, Auntie?

00:05:05.000 --> 00:05:06.439
Auntie has a favor to ask you.

00:05:07.120 --> 00:05:08.879
If Nana starts dating,

00:05:08.879 --> 00:05:10.079
you must tell Auntie.

00:05:10.480 --> 00:05:11.959
That child is too innocent.

00:05:11.959 --> 00:05:13.000
I'm afraid she'll get cheated.

00:05:14.240 --> 00:05:15.000
Auntie,

00:05:15.360 --> 00:05:16.279
don't worry.

00:05:16.439 --> 00:05:17.720
If she tells me she's dating,

00:05:17.959 --> 00:05:19.600
I'll definitely report to you immediately.

00:05:20.120 --> 00:05:20.759
Good, good, good.

00:05:22.040 --> 00:05:22.319
Come.

00:05:22.800 --> 00:05:24.120
Taste the meat Auntie made.

00:05:24.439 --> 00:05:25.920
Auntie, I really can't eat meat.

00:05:33.720 --> 00:05:35.160
Why does this always happen?

00:05:35.360 --> 00:05:36.680
Nana, can you stop pushing me?

00:05:38.480 --> 00:05:39.120
Nana.

00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:40.480
What's going on?

00:05:40.480 --> 00:05:41.079
Nana.

00:05:41.319 --> 00:05:42.120
Nana.

00:05:42.759 --> 00:05:44.079
Nana, open the door.

00:05:44.079 --> 00:05:45.959
Tell Mom what's wrong.

00:05:50.920 --> 00:05:52.240
I found Di Fu.

00:05:52.759 --> 00:05:53.519
I wanted to ask her.

00:05:53.519 --> 00:05:54.920
What on earth was wrong with Nana.

00:05:55.680 --> 00:05:56.720
Sure enough.

00:05:56.959 --> 00:05:58.399
Nana was dating someone.

00:05:58.920 --> 00:06:01.519
But she didn't know who Nana's boyfriend was either.

00:06:02.000 --> 00:06:04.879
When Di Fu and I returned home...

00:06:06.360 --> 00:06:08.720
Nana... Where could Nana go?

00:06:11.079 --> 00:06:11.480
Hello?

00:06:11.800 --> 00:06:12.839
The number you have dialed...

00:06:14.160 --> 00:06:15.240
Where could she go?

00:06:15.240 --> 00:06:16.759
Auntie, please don't panic yet.

00:06:16.759 --> 00:06:18.120
Nana will surely be fine.

00:06:18.399 --> 00:06:20.000
Where could she go?

00:06:26.759 --> 00:06:27.560
The password.

00:06:28.600 --> 00:06:30.000
You two are so close.

00:06:30.000 --> 00:06:31.600
You must know her password, right?

00:06:43.120 --> 00:06:43.759
It's open.

00:06:51.519 --> 00:06:52.720
Meet at the usual place.

00:06:53.879 --> 00:06:54.920
Who is this person?

00:06:56.959 --> 00:06:59.120
This must be the man Nana likes.

00:06:59.319 --> 00:07:00.519
No, I have to go find her.

00:07:00.519 --> 00:07:02.959
Auntie, where will you look?

00:07:03.720 --> 00:07:04.480
The usual place.

00:07:04.800 --> 00:07:06.560
Do you know where "the usual place" is?

00:07:09.480 --> 00:07:10.199
I'll go find her.

00:07:10.199 --> 00:07:11.920
Auntie, please calm down first, okay?

00:07:26.959 --> 00:07:27.519
Just as I thought.

00:07:28.279 --> 00:07:29.240
She has taxi records.

00:07:30.120 --> 00:07:31.519
Can we tell where she went?

00:07:34.160 --> 00:07:35.120
It should be here.

00:07:51.160 --> 00:07:52.519
The navigation says it's here.

00:07:57.120 --> 00:07:58.720
Di Fu, this place is so big.

00:07:58.720 --> 00:08:00.079
How are we going to find her?

00:08:00.279 --> 00:08:01.519
Auntie, you just...

00:08:01.519 --> 00:08:02.600
Don't worry yet.

00:08:04.079 --> 00:08:05.079
I'll go in and look first.

00:08:05.079 --> 00:08:06.120
You wait here for a moment.

00:08:10.519 --> 00:08:11.199
Nana.

00:08:12.319 --> 00:08:12.959
Nana.

00:08:13.519 --> 00:08:14.800
Nana? Is that you, Nana?

00:08:21.199 --> 00:08:21.920
Nana.

00:08:36.120 --> 00:08:38.000
Who are you? Give me back my daughter!

00:08:49.840 --> 00:08:50.440
Stop!

00:08:54.840 --> 00:08:55.679
Stop!

00:08:56.120 --> 00:08:57.519
Nana, stop!

00:09:00.720 --> 00:09:01.559
You, stop!

00:09:12.279 --> 00:09:12.960
Who are you?

00:09:14.639 --> 00:09:15.600
Don't come over here!

00:09:16.720 --> 00:09:18.720
I watched him walk towards me, step by step.

00:09:19.320 --> 00:09:19.919
Suddenly...

00:09:27.759 --> 00:09:29.000
Auntie! Auntie!

00:09:30.080 --> 00:09:30.720
Medicine.

00:09:31.000 --> 00:09:31.919
Pills... pills...

00:09:32.279 --> 00:09:32.799
Medicine.

00:09:33.000 --> 00:09:33.879
Auntie Ma Shan.

00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:35.279
You can't take any more pills.

00:09:35.279 --> 00:09:36.360
This medicine has side effects.

00:09:36.519 --> 00:09:37.919
Auntie, look at me.

00:09:38.000 --> 00:09:39.399
Look at me. Look at me.

00:09:39.639 --> 00:09:40.480
Deep breath.

00:09:41.279 --> 00:09:42.000
Inhale.

00:09:42.559 --> 00:09:43.200
Exhale.

00:09:47.159 --> 00:09:48.200
Deep breath.

00:09:50.279 --> 00:09:51.039
Good.

00:09:52.919 --> 00:09:53.759
Breathe again.

00:09:58.039 --> 00:09:59.399
Don't... don't fall asleep.

00:09:59.720 --> 00:10:00.919
The story isn't finished yet.

00:10:01.120 --> 00:10:02.559
Is her daughter dead or not?

00:10:03.200 --> 00:10:04.720
If her daughter wasn't dead...

00:10:05.240 --> 00:10:06.360
She wouldn't react like this.

00:10:08.480 --> 00:10:09.600
Where are you going, President Tan?

00:10:12.000 --> 00:10:12.799
Why stay here?

00:10:13.519 --> 00:10:14.480
To tuck her in?

00:10:15.679 --> 00:10:16.759
Let's go, let's go.

00:10:22.960 --> 00:10:24.000
So afterwards...

00:10:24.480 --> 00:10:26.840
Madam took on the responsibility of caring for Auntie Ma Shan.

00:10:28.480 --> 00:10:31.480
All these years, they were like mother and daughter.

00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:35.360
It's just a pity that now Madam...

00:10:35.799 --> 00:10:36.360
Miss Li.

00:10:37.279 --> 00:10:38.559
Did you study hypnosis?

00:10:38.960 --> 00:10:39.360
No.

00:10:39.759 --> 00:10:41.159
It's just that when I get agitated...

00:10:41.960 --> 00:10:43.200
I force myself to calm down.

00:10:43.759 --> 00:10:44.279
That's good.

00:10:54.600 --> 00:10:56.399
No one is allowed to enter the study.

00:10:58.000 --> 00:10:58.840
This is the rule Mr. Zhao

00:10:58.840 --> 00:11:00.360
established before he passed.

00:11:03.320 --> 00:11:06.320
My brother is dead. What rules?

00:11:06.879 --> 00:11:08.159
I'm his own brother.

00:11:08.159 --> 00:11:09.200
Can't I go in?

00:11:10.000 --> 00:11:12.200
Everyone, please move to the living room.

00:11:15.399 --> 00:11:16.320
That's enough, A Hai.

00:11:16.559 --> 00:11:17.440
I told you.

00:11:17.879 --> 00:11:18.720
Go to the living room.

00:11:19.480 --> 00:11:20.399
You insisted on coming here to take a look.

00:11:21.399 --> 00:11:22.200
And now?

00:11:22.399 --> 00:11:23.039
It's still early.

00:11:24.080 --> 00:11:24.639
Ms. Li.

00:11:25.480 --> 00:11:27.279
I'm very interested in your story.

00:11:27.519 --> 00:11:27.960
Next.

00:11:28.720 --> 00:11:30.080
I hope you can tell us about it.

00:11:31.159 --> 00:11:31.720
I refuse.

00:11:35.679 --> 00:11:36.360
Inspector Qi.

00:11:36.960 --> 00:11:37.559
Is this allowed?

00:11:47.960 --> 00:11:48.559
Ms. Li.

00:11:49.360 --> 00:11:51.919
You're the one who proposed the memorial.

00:11:52.759 --> 00:11:53.720
How come when it's your turn,

00:11:54.480 --> 00:11:55.639
you refuse?

00:11:57.120 --> 00:11:58.519
Because from your stories,

00:12:00.639 --> 00:12:02.039
I've heard nothing but lies.

00:12:03.399 --> 00:12:04.399
Hey, what do you mean by that?

00:12:05.480 --> 00:12:06.080
I know.

00:12:06.440 --> 00:12:08.279
You all want to clear yourselves of suspicion.

00:12:09.639 --> 00:12:10.799
I won't hold it against you.

00:12:11.480 --> 00:12:12.080
Anyway,

00:12:13.039 --> 00:12:14.200
if you still want to hear

00:12:14.200 --> 00:12:15.879
about the past between my sister and me,

00:12:16.120 --> 00:12:17.159
be a little more sincere.

00:12:18.120 --> 00:12:19.759
Don't try to fool me with lies.

00:12:21.120 --> 00:12:21.919
It's like this.

00:12:23.440 --> 00:12:25.600
President Tan and I don't know Di Fu well.

00:12:26.039 --> 00:12:27.960
If you want to hear stories about her,

00:12:27.960 --> 00:12:29.559
we really have nothing to share.

00:12:31.320 --> 00:12:32.600
Then talk about my brother-in-law.

00:12:33.320 --> 00:12:34.159
I really want to know

00:12:34.679 --> 00:12:36.000
exactly what kind of person he was.

00:12:47.879 --> 00:12:49.200
Sometimes I wonder,

00:12:51.879 --> 00:12:53.200
why it wasn't me who died.

00:12:55.840 --> 00:12:56.960
If it were possible,

00:12:59.600 --> 00:13:00.960
I would trade my life

00:13:03.200 --> 00:13:04.080
so my brother could live.